WWW-Formspring version 0.03
===========================

This Perl module is to facilitate development of Perl application
for the popular social networking website www.formspring.me

Currently it uses the beta API.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Carp
  LWP::UserAgent
  Moose
  Net::OAuth
  URI
  XML::Simple

